alfredsnippet.snippet:
CREATE TABLE tbl (
    id SERIAL NOT NULL,
    name VARCHAR(32),
    validity BOOLEAN NOT NULL DEFAULT true,
    words TEXT,
    create_at TIMESTAMP,
    version SMALLINT DEFAULT 1,
    PRIMARY KEY (id)
);
